description: Hubby's Dog House is doing it right, with the finest street fare you'll find in all of Chicago! This family-owned operation is doing justice to the classic Chicago dog while still shaking things up with a selection of fantastic Haute Dogs, Italian Beef, Beer Bratwurst, and more. Great food on the go, or the perfect caterers for all your most important events, Hubby's Dog House does it all!
name: Hubby's Dog House
